Jones Soda Co. couldn't be more proud of being 'your soda, your brand,' for twenty-one years. We adore your iconic customer-submitted photos adorning our retro glass bottles. We cherish the under-the-cap wisdoms telling our future on the daily. Bottle after bottle, we're committed to bringing you the most daring flavors, always sweetened with cane sugar  and keeping the voice of the consumer as our radically independent battle-cry. From the bottom of our cup, glass and can, Jones Soda Co. salutes YOU! Cheers to twenty-one more years together!












